Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.processor.pct_processor_time#value
Description: The percentage of elapsed time that the processor spends to execute a non-Idle thread

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.process.pct_processor_time#value
Description: The percentage of elapsed time that all of the process threads used the processor to execution instructions

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.memory.available_mbytes#value
Description: The amount of physical memory, in Megabytes, immediately available for allocation to a process or for system use.

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.process.private_bytes#value
Description: The current size, in bytes, of memory that this process has allocated that cannot be shared with other processes.

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.logicaldisk.c.pct_disk_time#value
Description: The percentage of elapsed time that the selected disk drive was busy servicing read or write requests.

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.logicaldisk.c.free_megabytes#value
Description: The unallocated space on the disk drive in megabytes

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.net_clr_memory.gen_1_heap_size#value
Description: Number of bytes in the .NET CLR garbage collector's generation 1 heap

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.net_clr_memory.gen_2_heap_size#value
Description: Number of bytes in the .NET CLR garbage collector's generation 2 heap

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.net_clr_memory.large_object_heap_size#value
Description: Number of bytes in the .NET CLR garbage collector's large object heap

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.net_clr_memory.gen_0_promoted_bytes_sec#value
Description: Rate at which bytes are being promoted by the .NET CLR garbage collector from the generation 0 heap to the generation 1 heap

Name: Telemetry.performance_counters.net_clr_memory.gen_1_promoted_bytes_sec#value
Description: Rate at which bytes are being promoted by the .NET CLR garbage collector from the generation 1 heap to the generation 2 heap

Name: Telemetry.data_core.data_source.io.all.out.$total#rate
Description: Rate of items read from all data sources

Name: Telemetry.data_core.data_source.io.all.in.$total#rate
Description: Rate of items written to all data sources

Name: Telemetry.data_core.data_source.operations.all.read.$total#rate
Description: Rate of read operations of all types on all data sources

Name: Telemetry.data_core.data_source.operations.all.write.$total#rate
Description: Rate of write operations of all types on all data sources

Name: Telemetry.data_core.script_engine.evaluation_time.csharpscriptengine#avg
Description: Average script evaluation time since startup
